Title: Makita DML811/2 DML811 LXT LED Worklight 14.4-18V/240V MAKDML811
Description:
The Makita DML811 LXT LED Worklight is the 240V version, and can be mounted on a tripod (NOT INCLUDED).

The Makita DML811 LXT LED Worklight can be powered by 18V/14.4V LXT batteries for cordless operation or plugged into the mains, available in both 110V and 240V versions.
The worklight is equipped with 30 LEDs, and three brightness settings; low, medium and high.
The DML811 can be mounted on to a tripod light stand (NOT included). 

Specifications:

Light Output: 3,000 Lumens.
Settings: Low/Medium/High.
Power Cord Length: 2.5m.
